requirement on key:
1. It can ONLY be a 32-bit hexadecimal number.
2. The letter in it should be uppercase.
requirement on message:
1. It can only be a 11-char string.
2. The last character can ONLY be one of "!.0123456789ABCD"
3. Other characters can ONLY be one of '0' - '9', 'a' - 'z', 'A' - 'Z', '!' and '.'
requirement on cipher:
1. It can only be a 11-char string.
2. The last character can ONLY be one of "!.0123456789ABCD"
3. Other characters can ONLY be one of '0' - '9', 'a' - 'z', 'A' - 'Z', '!' and '.'

Algorithm:
The program implements the IDEA (International Data Encryption Algorithm). For reference, https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Data_Encryption_Algorithm
Use a linear mapping to map ('!', '.', '0' - '9', 'a' - 'z', 'A' - 'Z') to (0 - 63).
